    <section id="api"><title>APIs</title>
      <p>HPE Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade is built on OpenStack technologies.</p>
      <p>The OpenStack REST API Documentation is open-source; both the published formats (PDF and
        HTML pages) as well as the docbook/wadl source documents. </p>
