                scope="external" format="pdf"><keyword keyref="kw-hcg-phrase"/> system
                administration</xref>. This document contains HPE Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade
              extensions to the OpenStack Compute API for use with the HCG 4.0 system. </p>
            <p>HPE Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade supports the following external REST APIs through
              its OAM floating IP address:</p>
